description: When the sun is shining it´s nice to have a walk near the Moldova river. First of all it´s beautiful. But even more because there are always hot boys hanging around. After a few minutes walk I saw a tall blond twink chilling at a boat rental. He was quite friendly when I started to ask him for a short interview. He was quite clever and he got my point very soon. Well, as I know that most boys in his age are desperate for some extra money I first asked him to sell me his undies. After that I offered him an even better deal. He wanted to know more but I insisted that we will continue our conversation on a short boat trip. Cause on a boat he can hardly run away. What can I say: he was shy but he had no chance.
title: Czech Hunter 43
